reviewText: I have quite a selection of exercise DVDs, but Mindy's workouts are my favorite!

Great video and my wife loves it!  She's a huge Mindy fan and she credits her videos with helping her get back into shape after having both our boys (3 yr old and 8 mo old).  My wife has all of her videos but wanted this one for the times where she may not be able to fit in a whole workout, but still wanted something that was going to give her the best workout possible in a compressed amount of time.
